*arvato Financial Solutions, Estonia, Data Miner/Data Scientist*
Tasks:
•    Build statistical / mathematical models based on big data or other data sources.
•    Make connections based on data and derive trends from that, e.g. what are recommended changes in the collection process based on analyzing data; how can fraud detection be optimized? What is the best consideration of variables to achieve the highest recognition in recognizing device fingerprints?
•    Ability to build scorecards and prognosis models.
•    Ability to bridge the world between technology oriented people and business people.
•    Develop quantitative and qualitative benchmarks based on data.
•    Advanced analytics based on trend topics and modern technologies, e.g. data lakes.

Requirements:
•    Bachelor degree, MBA degree – preference mathematics, statistic, engineering.
•    Experience in optimizing customer processes based on analytical work.
•    Technical skills to implement analysis, e.g. programming know-how, SAS, etc.
•    Practical experience in analyzing big data and data lakes is beneficial.
•    Fluent English, German is considered as a plus.

Other information:
•    Job located in Tallinn, Estonia. 
•    Relocation compensation.
•    Please be prepared for initial 1-2 months training in Germany and occasional business trips later.
:fork:  2500 - 3500EUR gross/month
For more information contact Kaido Hussar +372 56657749 or <mailto:kh@ctrl.ee|kh@ctrl.ee>
